#bscwomen #womenshealth #sayestothecup #menstrualcups #menstrualhygiene #menstrualhealth #bombae #getbombae #bombayshavingcompany

A normal day in the office turns into a fiery rap battle between two best friends trying to defend their choice of menstrual hygiene products. 

On one side we have Isha being an advocate for pads - she has been using them for the last 16 years but is unaware of the damage pads incite on the earth AND our purses. 

On the other hand we have Rushaki - a recent convert - repping menstrual cups. She believes that those days are gone when sanitary pads had monopolized the Indian menstrual market. 
 
Who emerges as the winner? Let us know in the comments.
